800
00:43:30,017 --> 00:43:31,017
Starting now.

801
00:43:31,046 --> 00:43:33,418
He's got one of those
little fancy Japanese toilet

802
00:43:33,453 --> 00:43:35,812
motion-sensor things
that spray the...

