he means that thing.

881
00:47:59,784 --> 00:48:01,246
Yes, obviously
he means that thing.

882
00:48:01,282 --> 00:48:03,013
Okay, where did you go?
I don't know.

883
00:48:03,048 --> 00:48:04,552
