No one has to get hurt.

900
00:48:36,856 --> 00:48:40,353
Wait, wait. His parents
are both lawyers.

901
00:48:40,388 --> 00:48:42,321
I mean, one is just
a personal injury lawyer,

902
00:48:42,356 --> 00:48:43,803
