954
00:50:47,646 --> 00:50:49,614
We're smaller than them,
but we're mobile.

955
00:50:49,650 --> 00:50:52,657
We have home field advantage
and a giant 3D printer.

956
00:50:52,692 --> 00:50:54,551
I say we get the gadgets,

957
00:50:54,586 --> 00:50:57,058
