968
00:51:17,082 --> 00:51:18,950
They're gonna kill
my brother. Give me that.

969
00:51:18,985 --> 00:51:21,250
Berger, I know you're
scared. I am, too.

970
00:51:21,285 --> 00:51:23,387
But we have a plan.
We can fight back. Shh.

971
