With all the asthma, the
celiacs, the tubs of Flonase?

979
00:51:43,041 --> 00:51:44,441
Guys, come on.
You guys are friends.

980
00:51:44,472 --> 00:51:46,441
We're risking our lives
for that rock

981
00:51:46,476 --> 00:51:48,372
